Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法弄  存儲器全被拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是事先廢棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都花了6年時間了  怎麼能空手而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據資料  這前面是19區域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寵物機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是訊息終端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞迪  我找到寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你幫忙分析數據
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與第一代及第二代的機體都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吠陀的資料中沒有的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有那樣的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有  我都親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親眼所見  親眼所見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似Gundam的MS至少有三台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和我們的太陽爐不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也釋放出了類似GN粒子的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  你們被那些Gundam給救下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師通過通訊說他們自己是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還若無其事地傳來了這些數據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是來打招呼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊可是前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人不是救了刹那他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情雖然是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見了面就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迎接新的Gundam Meister吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝影機捕捉到有物體靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示在主屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  讓Exia作出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  你對那艘船進行掃描
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷窺了  被偷窺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在提防我們吧  讓他們去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從靠近的船釋放出的  正是GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在船內確認有4台GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他們是怎麼弄到太陽爐的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  艙門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  妮娜  要抓緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所見到的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯  不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認來自MS的光通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在托勒密上著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們允許著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  解除Exia的待機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓刹那去簡報室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到著艦許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許著艦  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne一號機Gundam Meister  約翰·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne二號機Gundam Meister  邁克爾·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne三號機Gundam Meister  妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都好年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是親兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  Exia的機師是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia的Gundam Meister  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊  喜歡亂來的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡那一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  對我妹妹做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹的不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦  你這小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗嘗被砍的滋味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧  動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你  好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊  你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哈羅  哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  記憶喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  記憶喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  記憶喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  記憶喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  別待在這兒了  去房間談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙就是新的Gundam Meister…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和你的想法一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說出來我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫厲害的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  難道你對刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種Gundam  都沒聽爸爸媽媽提起過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼會擁有Gundam呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吠陀的數據庫中為什麼會沒有那種機體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有保守秘密的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐…不  GN Drive是從哪裡得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  無法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們來這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來看被舊時代的MS整得那麼慘的Meister們長啥樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不舒服  我去待機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會向吠陀彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊  如果是女人的話才不會理你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥  我感覺好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去船內轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓我生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  能不能告訴我們  你們用那Gundam做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你們一樣  我們也是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說  要和我們聯手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  誰會那麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你們只會綿軟地干涉  才會讓我們出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像所說的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無可奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不完美的改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  對於弟弟的無禮  我來賠罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  給我們下命令的人  是否對你們的武力干涉方法抱有疑問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們是閒置品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請繼續像以往那樣繼續作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將根據獨立的判斷進行干預
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對於伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的計劃而言是必須的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這將根據我們今後的行動而顯現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把Gundam交給那些傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  得讓吠陀驗證數據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的終端單元…開著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常地～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完了就拍屁股走人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個叫約翰的  相當不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  什麼時候拍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘機拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼讓他們離開行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本沒得到對方的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不儘然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們談話的時候  我調查了一下那種叫Throne的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是戰術預報員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用獨立終端把報告書發過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不要輸入吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  Exia的駕駛員是叫刹那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙有哪點好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得可愛嗎  我一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次遇到了把他打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任務了  有任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要讓世界知道Celestial Being的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的重要情報  李本茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得感謝神讓我遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣你才撿我回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那次相遇是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我會成為Celestial Being的監視者也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對世界怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎麼樣  我只是監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是注視世界的變化的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完了  定期測試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真累人啊  還要兼職打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試前暫停不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲你還好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個  考完休息這段時間做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想看的電影什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉  我要回趟西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要參加表哥的結婚典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  好好放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不許花心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不許花心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到處採訪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎  各個陣營的正式聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說被重創的MS累計87台  而戰死者則超過了200人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  根據當時在場的士兵的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有新的Gundam出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是可靠情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來Celestial Being還留了一手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那個士兵的名字和所屬部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是池田那裡傳來的小道消息  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上聯絡  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:27.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}聯合軍  太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅沒能完成接到的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還失去了三名優秀的Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不配當隊長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也沒想到會有新型Gundam出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且本來性能差距就大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有和Gundam性能相同的機體的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag是我軍的最新銳的機體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利爾  我們是Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出風度來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  有從大氣層突入的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  預測的降落點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}聯合  美國  MSWAD基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我的假說一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的能源發生器是利用了拓撲缺陷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就都能解釋得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之所以只有幾台  以及需要200年以上的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能製造那種能源發生器的環境是木星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120年前的載人木星探測計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個計劃和Gundam的開發有牽連嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的真正目的不是根除戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你知道的太多了…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測室通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台可能是Gundam的MS由DW9877方向朝本基地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體MS部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向各基地請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不明物體進入可視範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些Gundam…是新型號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  開始鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣殲滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高濃度GN粒子  傳輸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…目標是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子  傳輸完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Eins  GN MEGA Launcher  射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo  厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘍囉們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  有3台新型號的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授…埃夫曼教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是忍無可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩一下嘛  老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一會兒就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們破壞  蹂躪並全滅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一下  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Flag的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會被幹掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎麼可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德·梅森！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  Flag…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是Fang哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩夠了嗎  該撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面還有任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister可都是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要盲目追過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要讓我丟面子丟到什麼地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙襲擊了美軍的基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不詳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀好像也沒什麼消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～  盡做些讓我們更招風的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…真的是Gundam Meister嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點哦  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向你爸爸媽媽問好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告別之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈你也真是的  太在意別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還是這樣的沙慈好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有著相同的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那樣的我們也已過了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交錯的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無法接受並急躁著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}捨棄了無用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}給予這世界以溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便顯示出勇氣　即便逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一個人亦是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心靈深處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延續...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由於不可忘記　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要離去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還要留在這廣闊大地同伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有什麼信念和理念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在戰場上逝去的是人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又有誰落下了眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「惡意的矛頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  否定Gundam


